title: dogs or cats were made first?

messages.content: dogs or cats were made first?

It's difficult to determine which was created first because dogs and cats evolved independently over millions of years, rather than being directly created by any known creator. However, the earliest dog-like animals emerged around 42 million years ago (the Eocene epoch), while the earliest cat-like animal fossils date back approximately 25 million years.
